        <abstract> 
<p>Reminds CD of earlier promise to permit extracts of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> to be translated and published in EA’s <hi rend="italic">Revue Scientifique</hi> once entire work is printed. Book appeared weeks ago, so EA again requests permission. <hi rend="italic">Revue</hi> has been appearing irregularly owing to war with Germans.</p> 
